title: Waimata
text:
Waimata is a rural community in the <a href="Hauraki%20District">Hauraki District</a> and <a href="Waikato">Waikato</a> region of New Zealand's <a href="North%20Island">North Island</a>.
The population of Waimata and its surrounds was 138 people in 54 households in the <a href="2013%20New%20Zealand%20census">2013 New Zealand census</a>.
